{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean-- I mean, this was quite separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but as far as respected, or-- the business people in our town, especially my family, were respected by the non-Jewish people as honest-- honest traders.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the professional people, they were the best doctors, the best solicitors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had quite a good relationship with the non-Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism usually was only from other schoolchildren, from the non-Jewish schoolchildren, sort of Jew-baiting, name calling, which we ignored.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you have to be-- have to be careful, especially-- especially on Easters, when there was all-- from the Catholic church, there was a procession.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they said the Jewish people should better stay indoors, because-- because a priest usually talked about it, how-- how their God has been crucified.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they were-- some of the ignorant persons, they were liable to break some Jewish windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But otherwise, I haven't felt-- myself, I never involved an anti-Semitic incident, though there was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't affect me directly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The childhood generally was quite happy and contented childhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My first experience as a child, I remember-- I remember the Anschluss, which was 1938, where Austria was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And really, I remember the worried faces in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I asked what-- what went on, then they said that the-- that the Germans had occupied Austria, which is just our next door, considering we were very close to the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by that time, we knew about Hitler, because that was one of the-- how they were taunting us, the non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler is coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hitler Is coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I had in childhood a fear that there's somebody horrible, Hitler, who eventually is going to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
